summary: An ordinance accepting deeds from Henriette Havers and G. Havers, her husband, Mike McDonald and Delia McDonald, husband and wife, Mary M. McRae and Daniel D. McRae, her husband, C. S. Hufford and Mabel Hufford, his wife, Perry C. Johnson, widower, and Fred Chidester and Mrs. Fred Chidester, his wife, to the City of Seattle, and laying off 39th Avenue Southwest.
